Dolph Sweet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dolph_Sweet 0 Adolphus Jean Sweet (July 18, 1920 – May 8, 1985) was an American actor, credited with nearly 60 television and film roles as well as several roles in stage productions before his death from cancer in 1985.
